Configure Call Transcription

Service Cloud Voice supports real-time transcription with Amazon Transcribe, Contact Lens for Amazon Connect, or partner telephony provider. Transcripts are displayed in the Enhanced Conversation component.

This feature is available with SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH AMAZON CONNECT, SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY FROM AMAZON CONNECT, and SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY.

For setup information, see Set Up Call Transcription. All audio on the customer's side is recorded when enabling transcription with Amazon Transcribe or Contact Lens for Amazon Connect.

For a list of supported languages, see Amazon Transcribe's Transcription Languages Supported by Service Cloud Voice and Amazon documentation for Contact Lens.

For Amazon Transcribe questions and support, contact Amazon Web Services.
title: Configuring Call Transcription in Service Cloud
